## 5. ì„œë¸Œì¿¼ë¦¬

### SELECTì ˆ
```sql
SELECT name, population, (SELECT AVG(population) FROM country)
FROM country;
```

### WHEREì ˆ
```sql
SELECT *
FROM country
WHERE population > (SELECT AVG(population) FROM country);
```

### FROMì ˆ
```sql
SELECT *
FROM employees e
INNER JOIN (SELECT * FROM dept_manager WHERE to_date='9999-01-01') t
USING(emp_no);
```

### ì˜ˆ: ë§¤ë‹ˆì € ì´ë¦„ê³¼ ê·¼ì†ë…„ìˆ˜
```sql
SELECT dept_no, first_name, last_name, AGE(CURRENT_DATE, from_date)
FROM dept_manager INNER JOIN employees USING(emp_no);
```

